In children with HIV infection，some of these signs may not be present，and the diagnosis of measles may be difficult．

\section*{6．4．1 Severe complicated measles}

\section*{Diagnosis}

In a child with evidence of measles（as above），any one of the following symptoms and signs indicates the presence of severe complicated measles：
－inability to drink or breastfeed
－vomits everything
